98
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:50,680
having extra time, or having
time is a little different.

99
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,960
And it's the phrase, time to kill.

100
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,360
This is a phrase you would use

101
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:57,300
