or once in a blue moon.

173
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,900
Let me give you some example sentences.

174
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:46,490
Every once in a while, we take
the kids out for ice cream.

175
00:06:46,490 --> 00:06:47,970
That means we don't do it every day,

176
