178
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:55,560
Every once in a while, we take
the kids out for ice cream.

179
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:58,310
Another phrase we use is the
phrase from time to time.

180
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,400
And I can say this, from time to time,

181
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,160
Jen and I go out on a date.

182
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,350
From time to time, we
leave the kids at home,

183
00:07:04,350 --> 00:07:06,310
and we go out with just the two of us

184
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:08,210
for a meal, and maybe to see a movie.

185
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:12,290
So from time to time means I
guess every other month or so,

186
00:07:12,290 --> 00:07:13,550
maybe every three months.

187
00:07:13,550 --> 00:07:16,890
There's no specific time
attached to these phrases.

188
00:07:16,890 --> 00:07:18,920
And then the phrase once in a blue moon.

189
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,760
When I was younger,

190
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:22,170
I went and saw movies with
my friends all the time,

191
00:07:22,170 --> 00:07:24,480
